1) Hover can't be possible in UI mode in Behat.
2) HTML reports can't be generated in behat >3.0.0
3) In UI mode, if you looking for any text it wont search by implicit method of
"Then I should see text matching"  instead it searches with "Then i should see" - unknown error
4) We can't see status code in Browser mode because it is not available in selenium2Driver
5) Sometimes the feature file wont run with goutte driver, it will work if you add "www." prefix to your url like "http://"www"url" and issue will be resolved the issue is not known yet!!
